{
  "stem": "27509.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I find it hard to give you an answer on that one for a very simple reason-- because the life in Bialystok-- as indeed in most Jewish towns-- was so integrated in terms of the Jewish self-- self-management in-- in-- on every level, whether it is in-- in-- in social or in-- or-- or in economic or in-- in public or whatever it is that there was hardly-- there was hardly any-- any contact between the Polish population and the Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 82
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the smaller towns where-- where-- the-- where the--the-- the immediate physical contact and the economic interaction was much more prevalent-- because in the little townships where they lived, the-- the-- the middlemen of-- in agrarian products or-- or in building roads or things like that, they had direct contact with the-- with-- with the peasant trade.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the big cities, especially in times like that, you-- you didn't-- you didn't see a-- a-- a-- a--an-- a-- a Polish person, really.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to go to a certain definite place where you know you would see a Polish person.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am not quite clear about this question.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- the first real signs of danger of-- of-- of the oncoming tragedy was the Stalin-- the Molotov-Ribbentrop Pact.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The minute that pact was signed, there was no question anymore that-- that war is coming, because--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the issue was at that-- at that stage-- at that stage, everybody knew that-- that-- that Hitler is ready to strike.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was afraid that whichever way he will go, he doesn't want to have to fight on two fronts.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No-- no politician, no general is-- is prepared for that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now there is an exception.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
